subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal called for the trainer on numerous occasions during his somewhat contentious 6-4, 4-6, 6-7 (5), 6-2, 6-3 victory against Philipp Petzschner in the third round.
